name: HACHI HACHI Forever
description:
The mighty infinite "88" is a powerful current of energy wave that brings flourishing happiness and wealth. Keep it running and it will nature the soul, decompose the stress.

It is the representation of calling and receiving, the breath of ying and yang. Where we find peace we find madness, and between waves of emotions we take our source of thought and vision to the next relative dimentions. Only when there is enough flow, the lights shine, the lives intertwine, the kindle shapes the hive.
